The Steve Tshwete district currently has 671 positive cases with 226 recoveries and three Covid-19 related deaths. eMalahleni – 1901. Govan Mbeki – 954. Mbombela – 799. •According to the Department of Health, the Steve Tshwete district only recorded three fatalities so far. It could however be confirmed that five people who tested positive for Covid-19 have died.